# Lean IDS - AI Assistant Rules
# This file provides guidelines for AI coding assistants (Cursor, Windsurf, Cline, etc.)

## � IMPORTANT: READ THESE FILES FIRST (IN ORDER)

**⚠️ BEFORE writing ANY code, you MUST read these files in this exact order:**

1. **AI_READING_FLOW.md** - Master reading flow (START HERE)
2. **This file (.cursorrules)** - Core rules (you're reading it now)
3. **AI_GUIDELINES.md** - Complete universal guidelines
