## �🚨 CRITICAL RULES - MUST FOLLOW

### 1. LIBRARY USAGE - STRICT ENFORCEMENT
**RULE: Use ONLY Lean IDS components. NO external UI libraries allowed.**

#### ✅ ALLOWED:
- Import from `@lean-ids/components`
- Import from `@lean-ids/tokens`
- Import from `@lean-ids/icons`
- Use existing libraries already in package.json (React, styled-components, etc.)

#### ❌ FORBIDDEN:
- Material-UI (MUI)
- Ant Design
- Chakra UI
- Bootstrap
- Tailwind UI components
- Shadcn/ui
- Radix UI
- Mantine
- Any other external UI component library

#### 🔄 OVERRIDE RULE:
If user explicitly says "use only Lean IDS" or "replace with Lean IDS":
- Remove existing external UI library imports
- Replace with equivalent Lean IDS components
- Update package.json to remove unused dependencies

#### 💡 EXAMPLES:

**❌ WRONG:**
```tsx
import { Button } from '@mui/material';
import { Input } from 'antd';
```

**✅ CORRECT:**
```tsx
import { Button, Input } from '@lean-ids/components';
```

**❌ WRONG (Fresh Project):**
```tsx
// User creates new component
import { Card } from '@chakra-ui/react';
```

**✅ CORRECT (Fresh Project):**
```tsx
// User creates new component
import { Card } from '@lean-ids/components';
```

