## 🎨 PAGE TEMPLATES GUIDELINES

### Template 1: Top Bar Only
```tsx
<PageLayout
  variant="topbar-only"
  pageTitle="Page Title"
  pageDescription="Optional description"
  breadcrumbs={[...]}
  topHeader={{
    appName: "App Name",
    showLogo: true,
    menuItems: [...],
    userInitials: "AB",
    userAvatarUrl: "..."
  }}
  footer={{
    lastUpdated: "...",
    version: "...",
    feedbackText: "...",
    feedbackUrl: "..."
  }}
>
  {/* Content */}
</PageLayout>
```

### Template 2: Sidebar Only
```tsx
<PageLayout
  variant="sidebar-only"
  pageTitle="Page Title"
  breadcrumbs={[...]}
  sideNav={{
    groups: [...],
    user: {...},
    isPinned: false,
    onPinChange: (pinned) => {...}
  }}
>
  {/* Content */}
</PageLayout>
```

### Template 3: Top Bar + Sidebar
```tsx
<PageLayout
  variant="topbar-sidebar"
  pageTitle="Page Title"
  breadcrumbs={[...]}
  topHeader={{
    appName: "App Name",
    menuItems: [...],
    userInitials: "AB"
  }}
  sideNav={{
    groups: [...],
    user: {...},
    isPinned: false,
    onPinChange: (pinned) => {...}
  }}
>
  {/* Content */}
</PageLayout>
```

